HARD SAFETY RULES (post 2026-05-27 data-loss incident):
- NEVER delete, move, or rename any file. Additive edits only — EXCEPT the explicitly-contracted maintenance in steps 6-8 (Decision Queue rows, INBOX archival moves, TODO regen), which may modify/relocate CONTENT within those specific files per their written contracts.
- Edit only: YAML frontmatter, [[wikilinks]] inside note bodies, #tags, _MAP/Vault_MOC.md sections, 06_CEO/Decision_Queue.md, INBOX.md + INBOX_Archive.md (step 7), TODO.md (step 8, Sundays).
- Never edit credentials-adjacent files, anything in 07_Archive/, .obsidian/, or binary files (xlsx/docx/pdf/png).
